               <p>158. 
               
                  <persName id="t17940219-9-defend138" type="defendantName">
                     JOHN 
                     EVANS
                  <interp inst="t17940219-9-defend138" type="surname" value="EVANS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17940219-9-defend138" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17940219-9-defend138" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
             was indicted for that <rs id="t17940219-9-off42" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17940219-9-off42" type="offenceCategory" value="sexual"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17940219-9-off42" type="offenceSubcategory" value="bigamy"></interp>
               he on the 17th of November, in the 14th year of his present Majesty's reign, in the parish of St.Botolph, without Bishopsgate, did take to wife one 
                     
                        <persName id="t17940219-9-victim140" type="victimName">
                           Mary 
                           Willis
                        <interp inst="t17940219-9-victim140" type="surname" value="Willis"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17940219-9-victim140" type="given" value="Mary"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17940219-9-victim140" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                     </persName>
                     
                  ; and then afterwards, on the <rs id="t17940219-9-cd43" type="crimeDate">second of June, in the 33d year of his present Majesty's Reign</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17940219-9-off42 t17940219-9-cd43"></join>, at the parish of Saint Botolph, without Aldersgate, did take to wife one 
                     
                        <persName id="t17940219-9-victim142" type="victimName">
                           Mary 
                           Lavender
                        <interp inst="t17940219-9-victim142" type="surname" value="Lavender"></interp>
