                        <interp inst="t17940219-9-victim142" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                     </persName>
                     
                  , and was then and there married to her, the aforesaid 
                     <persName id="t17940219-9-person143">
                        Mary
                         Willis
                     <interp inst="t17940219-9-person143" type="surname" value="Willis"></interp>
